      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·谷風之什·008.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">鼓鍾.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>鼓鍾將將，淮水湯湯。憂心且傷。淑人君子，懷允不忘。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>His bells ring out jiang-jiang,
While the waters of the Huai go sweeping on;
Sad is my heart and wouded.
The virtuous sovereigns of old, --
In my heart, indeed, I cannot forget them.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-gufeng-008__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
