      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·谷風之什·008.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">鼓鍾.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>鼓鍾喈喈，淮水湝湝。憂心且悲。淑人君子，其德不回。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>His drums ring out jie-jie,
While the waters of the Huai rush along;
My heart is sad and grieved.
Of the virtuous sovereigns of old,
The virtue was without flaw.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-gufeng-008__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
