      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·谷風之什·008.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">鼓鍾.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>鼓鍾伐鼛，淮有三洲。憂心且妯。淑人君子，其德不猶。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>His bells ring out, his large drums resound,
There are the three islands in the Huai;
Sad is my heart and moved.
Of the virtuous sovereigns of old,
The virtue was different from this.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
