      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·谷風之什·008.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">鼓鍾.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>鼓鍾欽欽，鼓瑟鼓琴。笙磬同音。以雅以南，以籥不僭。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>His bells ring out qin-qin;
His lutes, large and small, give their notes;
The tones of his organs and sounding stones are in unison.
They sing the Ya and the Nan,
Dancing to their flutes without error.</seg>
      </tuv>
